data.description: Presenting an exceptional opportunity to acquire a renovated 3 bedroom 2 bathroom residence, spanning nearly 2,000 square feet, in the esteemed North Woodlake neighborhood. This home has undergone recent upgrades, including new flooring, roof, energy efficient windows, and a fully paid-for solar system, enhancing its eco-friendly appeal.  Nestled on an expansive 10,000 + square foot corner lot, this property offers versatile options, from additional parking space to convenient storage solutions. We invite you to experience the elegance and functionality of this remarkable home. Don't miss your chance to explore this splendid property in person
